{"type":"text","timestamp":1773437492901,"sessionID":"ses_316e48c38ffe75SZrvzMc1U3SN","part":{"id":"prt_ce91c29e2001SQ5rp7JYXdSBGJ","sessionID":"ses_316e48c38ffe75SZrvzMc1U3SN","messageID":"msg_ce91c17ec001lucJhrvzdzKr44","type":"text","text":"## Goal\n\nWire TOON output format as a third option into all CLI commands that already support `--output json`. Update schema introspection to advertise toon support. This is feature `toon-wire-commands` on branch `feature/toon-wire-commands`.\n\n## Instructions\n\n- Use conventional commits with scope `toon-wire-commands`\n- Commit after each logical unit of work (not one big squash)\n- Do NOT push to remote or modify `tasks/` directory\n- Run `bun run build` at the end to verify everything works\n- Use `bun dev` (not the global `wombo` binary) for testing\n- Always use `portless run` when starting any localhost server\n\n## Discoveries\n\nAfter thoroughly reading the entire codebase, here is the current state of TOON support:\n\n### Already fully wired (TOON renderer provided as 4th arg to `output()`):\n- **`tasks list`** (`src/commands/tasks/list.ts`) — uses `renderTasksList()` ✅\n- **`tasks show`** (`src/commands/tasks/show.ts`) — uses `renderTaskShow()` ✅\n- **`tasks check`** (`src/commands/tasks/check.ts`) — uses `renderTasksCheck()` ✅\n- **`status`** (`src/commands/status.ts`) — uses `renderStatus()` ✅\n- **`history`** (`src/commands/history.ts`) — uses `renderHistoryList()` / `renderHistoryDetail()` ✅\n- **`describe`** (`src/index.ts`) — has special TOON path using `renderToonLegend()` / `buildToonSpec()` ✅\n\n### Core output infrastructure already supports TOON:\n- `src/lib/output.ts` — `resolveOutputFormat()` already handles `\"toon\"`, `output()` accepts optional `toonRenderer` 4th arg, `outputError()` and `outputMessage()` already handle TOON format\n- `src/lib/toon.ts` — Has specific renderers + `renderGeneric()` fallback\n- `src/lib/toon-spec.ts` — Has `TOON_COMMAND_SPECS` array with specs for `tasks list`, `tasks show`, `status`, `history`\n\n### Commands that need TOON wiring (use `output()` but don't pass a toonRenderer):\n1. **`abort`** (`src/commands/abort.ts`) — calls `output()` with no toonRenderer\n2. **`cleanup`** (`src/commands/cleanup.ts`) — calls `output()` with no toonRenderer (2 call sites: dry-run and real)\n3. **`verify`** (`src/commands/verify.ts`) — calls `output()` with no toonRenderer; also has `renderVerify()` in toon.ts but it's not wired\n4. **`merge`** (`src/commands/merge.ts`) — calls `output()` with no toonRenderer (2 call sites: dry-run and real)\n5. **`retry`** (`src/commands/retry.ts`) — calls `output()` with no toonRenderer (3 call sites)\n6. **`launch`** (`src/commands/launch.ts`) — uses `outputError`/`outputMessage` which already handle TOON, but some direct `output()` calls may lack toonRenderer\n7. **`logs`** (`src/commands/logs.ts`) — calls `output()` with no toonRenderer; follow mode has special JSON handling but no TOON\n8. **`tasks graph`** (`src/commands/tasks/graph.ts`) — has special `fmt === \"json\"` branch but no TOON handling\n\n### Commands using only `outputMessage`/`outputError` (already TOON-aware, no work needed):\n- `tasks add`, `tasks set-status`, `tasks set-priority`, `tasks set-difficulty`, `tasks archive` — these use `outputMessage()`/`outputError()` which already handle TOON\n\n### Schema introspection needs:\n- `src/lib/schema.ts` line 88: `--output` flag description says \"Output format: text (default) or json\" — needs updating to mention toon\n- `src/lib/toon-spec.ts` `TOON_COMMAND_SPECS` array: needs new entries for `verify`, `abort`, `cleanup`, `merge`, `retry`, `logs`, `tasks graph`\n\n## Accomplished\n\n- **Read all relevant files** — Complete understanding of the codebase architecture\n- **No code changes made yet** — Still in analysis phase\n- **No TODO plan created yet**\n\n## Relevant files / directories\n\n### Core output/format infrastructure:\n- `src/lib/output.ts` — Output format resolution, `output()`, `outputError()`, `outputMessage()` helpers\n- `src/lib/toon.ts` — TOON renderers: `renderTasksList`, `renderTaskShow`, `renderStatus`, `renderVerify`, `renderHistoryList`, `renderHistoryDetail`, `renderTasksCheck`, `renderGeneric`\n- `src/lib/toon-spec.ts` — TOON format spec, encode/decode helpers, `TOON_COMMAND_SPECS`, `buildToonSpec()`, `renderToonLegend()`\n- `src/lib/schema.ts` — Command registry, `GLOBAL_FLAGS` (line 83-98), `commandToSchema()`, `allCommandSchemas()`\n\n### Commands needing TOON wiring:\n- `src/commands/abort.ts` — needs toonRenderer in `output()` call\n- `src/commands/cleanup.ts` — needs toonRenderer in 2 `output()` calls\n- `src/commands/verify.ts` — needs toonRenderer; `renderVerify()` exists but is not wired\n- `src/commands/merge.ts` — needs toonRenderer in 2 `output()` calls\n- `src/commands/retry.ts` — needs toonRenderer in 3 `output()` calls\n- `src/commands/launch.ts` — large file, uses outputError/outputMessage (already handled)\n- `src/commands/logs.ts` — needs toonRenderer in `output()` call + follow mode TOON support\n- `src/commands/tasks/graph.ts` — needs TOON branch alongside existing JSON branch\n\n### Commands already wired (for reference):\n- `src/commands/status.ts` ✅\n- `src/commands/history.ts` ✅\n- `src/commands/tasks/list.ts` ✅\n- `src/commands/tasks/show.ts` ✅\n- `src/commands/tasks/check.ts` ✅\n\n### Commands using outputMessage only (already TOON-aware):\n- `src/commands/tasks/add.ts` ✅\n- `src/commands/tasks/set-status.ts` ✅\n- `src/commands/tasks/set-priority.ts` ✅\n- `src/commands/tasks/set-difficulty.ts` ✅\n- `src/commands/tasks/archive.ts` ✅\n\n### Entry point:\n- `src/index.ts` — CLI arg parsing, command routing, `describe` command TOON handling\n\n### Config:\n- `package.json` — build script: `bun run build`","time":{"start":1773437492899,"end":1773437492899}}}
