{"type":"text","timestamp":1773437770742,"sessionID":"ses_316e48c38ffe75SZrvzMc1U3SN","part":{"id":"prt_ce920c5a2001HfjG1Y343Z45Lr","sessionID":"ses_316e48c38ffe75SZrvzMc1U3SN","messageID":"msg_ce920be22001F42JzilRByWuoL","type":"text","text":"Now I need to add TOON handling to the graph command. Looking at the command flow:\n1. Empty graph → uses `output()` (needs toonRenderer)\n2. `--mermaid` → uses `output()` (needs toonRenderer)\n3. `--output json` → has custom JSON branch\n4. Default text rendering\n\nI need to add a TOON branch and wire toonRenderers:","time":{"start":1773437770742,"end":1773437770742}}}
