{"type":"text","timestamp":1773437980853,"sessionID":"ses_316e48c38ffe75SZrvzMc1U3SN","part":{"id":"prt_ce923e7a5001wQiX3D6pIsJOd3","sessionID":"ses_316e48c38ffe75SZrvzMc1U3SN","messageID":"msg_ce923dc11001ytZFjOPY697NUf","type":"text","text":"Everything is complete. Here's a summary of what was accomplished:\n\n## Summary\n\n### 2 commits on `feature/toon-wire-commands`:\n\n**Commit 1: `feat(toon-wire-commands): wire TOON renderers into all operational commands`**\n- Added 8 new TOON-specific renderers in `src/lib/toon.ts`:\n  - `renderAbort()` — key:value format for abort results\n  - `renderCleanup()` — key:value format supporting both dry-run and real cleanup\n  - `renderMerge()` — tabular format with `#MERGE` header, supporting dry-run\n  - `renderRetry()` — key:value format supporting dry-run, interactive, and headless modes\n  - `renderLogs()` — `#LOGS` header + raw log lines\n  - `renderLaunchDryRun()` — `#LAUNCH` header + tabular feature listing\n  - `renderGraph()` — `#GRAPH` header + optional mermaid source + orphan table\n  - `renderVerifyResults()` — `#VERIFY` header + tabular agent results\n- Wired toonRenderer (4th arg) into `output()` calls in:\n  - `abort.ts` (1 call site)\n  - `cleanup.ts` (2 call sites: dry-run and real)\n  - `verify.ts` (1 call site)\n  - `merge.ts` (2 call sites: dry-run and real)\n  - `retry.ts` (3 call sites: dry-run, interactive, headless)\n  - `logs.ts` (1 call site + follow mode TOON handling)\n  - `tasks/graph.ts` (2 `output()` calls + new `fmt === \"toon\"` branch)\n  - `launch.ts` (1 dry-run call site)\n\n**Commit 2: `feat(toon-wire-commands): update schema introspection and TOON specs for all commands`**\n- Updated `GLOBAL_FLAGS` `--output` description: `\"text (default) or json\"` → `\"text (default), json, or toon\"`\n- Updated `tasks check` `--output` flag description similarly\n- Added 8 new `TOON_COMMAND_SPECS` entries for: `verify`, `abort`, `cleanup`, `merge`, `retry`, `logs`, `tasks graph`, `launch`\n\n### Build verification\n- `bun run typecheck` ✅ (clean, no errors)\n- `bun run build` ✅ (1.00 MB bundle, 157 modules)","time":{"start":1773437980852,"end":1773437980852}}}
